snippet.title: Best VGM 1654 - Galactic Pinball - Alien
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 768 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gt-QIiYkAOU

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Virtual Boy
Galactic Pinball (1995)
Alien
Kenji Yamamoto & Masaru Tajima
